            "text": "was",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " Sheba, the son of Bichri, a Benjamite: and he blew a trumpet, and said, We have no part in ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cverse3",
            "text": "{b}",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " David, neither have we inheritance in the son ",
