        "text": "(b) As they of Judah say.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(c) He thought by speaking contemptuously of the king, to stir the people farther to sedition, or else by causing Israel to depart, thought that they of Judah would have esteemed him less.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
